title: Response to Rebel Wisdom Ken Wilber/JBP Part 2 - Jon Haidt, Julian Jaynes, Paul Vanderklay
description:
There are many more things to discuss about this interview. In this video, I focus on a few aspects of the second half of the video, including the issue of masculine/feminine, is morality progressive? what does mythic consciousness feel like? Like Julian Jaynes' Bicameralism? Waking up versus a subject/object view of God.

Paul VanderKlay on the same video: https://youtu.be/NL1-O07oMvM
Zamm Audiobook channel: https://youtu.be/ClA9wO8GaqQ
